data.text:
Delaney Bramlett and Bonnie Bramlett were married for 5 years. They dated for 1 year after getting together in 1966 and married in 1967. 5 years later they divorced in 1972.

They had a daughter named Rebecca Ruth age 56.

About

American Musician Delaney Bramlett was born Delaine Alvin "Delaney" Bramlett on 1st July, 1939 in Pontotoc, Mississippi, USA and passed away on 27th Dec 2008 Los Angeles, California, USA aged 69. He is most remembered for Single: Guess I Must Be Dreamin. His zodiac sign is Cancer.

Bonnie Bramlett is a 79 year old American Singer. Born Bonnie Lynn O'Farrell on 8th November, 1944 in Granite City, Illinois, USA, she is famous for Bonnie Watkins on Roseanne, musical duo Delaney & Bonnie. Her zodiac sign is Scorpio.
